        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com" target="_blank">
            <img src="https://cdn2.iconfinder.com/data/icons/social-media-2285/512/1_Linkedin_unofficial_colored_svg-512.png" alt="LinkedIn Logo" width="30" height="30">
        </a>
        <p>&copy; 2024 OnlyAuth. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
